column5: I was reading some of the recent topics and thought I would experiment with posting photos from photobucket. Back to fishing.  Some photos from Manitouwabing and Couchiching.  That was weird, it allowed access to all photos on photobucket. Sorry, I deleted the link.
Think you need to change your privacy settings in Photobucket for that not to happen.
Thanks bobowski, I think I got it figured out with a little search on the internet.
